sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Claude as Claude Code
    participant Load as load_project_context
    participant Plan as plan_increment
    participant Proto as generate_prototype
    participant Handoff as handoff_to_claude_dev
    participant Update as update_project_context
    participant FS as File System
    participant V0 as v0 API

    Note over User,V0: MCP Workflow (5 Steps) - Incremental Development

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over User,Load: Step 1: Load Project Context
        User->>Claude: Load project context
        Claude->>Load: load_project_context(context_path)
        Load->>FS: Read project-context.json
        FS-->>Load: Context data<br/>(features, routes, components)
        Load->>Load: Validate & parse context
        Load-->>Claude: ✅ Context loaded<br/>(features, routes, patterns)
        Claude-->>User: Show project summary
    end

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note over User,Plan: Step 2: Plan Increment
        User->>Claude: "Add Global Configuration page"
        Claude->>Plan: plan_increment(project_context, feature_request)
        Plan->>Plan: Analyze existing patterns
        Plan->>Plan: Find similar features
        Plan->>Plan: Determine generation scope<br/>(full_app vs content_only)
        Plan->>Plan: Identify reusable components
        Plan-->>Claude: ✅ Increment plan<br/>(scope, references, sections)
        Claude-->>User: Show plan with references
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over User,Proto: Step 3: Generate Prototype
        User->>Claude: Generate from plan
        Claude->>Proto: generate_prototype(context from plan)
        Proto->>V0: POST /prototype with context

        loop For each screen
            V0-->>Proto: Stream progress
            Proto-->>Claude: Update progress
            Claude-->>User: Screen N/M generated
        end

        V0-->>Proto: Complete prototype
        Proto-->>Claude: ✅ Prototype done<br/>(screens, components, preview)
        Claude-->>User: Show preview link
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 245)
        Note over User,Handoff: Step 4: Implementation Brief
        User->>Claude: Create implementation brief
        Claude->>Handoff: handoff_to_claude_dev(prototype_id, result, context)
        Handoff->>Handoff: Extract UX patterns<br/>Component list<br/>Implementation rules
        Handoff-->>Claude: ✅ Brief created
        Claude-->>User: Show implementation brief
    end

    Note over User,Update: [Claude Dev implements the feature]

    rect rgb(250, 240, 255)
        Note over User,Update: Step 5: Update Project Context
        User->>Claude: Feature implemented, update context
        Claude->>Update: update_project_context(context_path, feature_update)
        Update->>FS: Read current context
        FS-->>Update: Current context
        Update->>Update: Mark feature as done<br/>Add routes<br/>Add components<br/>Add patterns
        Update->>FS: Write updated context
        FS-->>Update: Saved
        Update-->>Claude: ✅ Context updated<br/>(new routes, components)
        Claude-->>User: Show updated project state
    end

    Note over User,V0: Ready for next feature (context preserved)
